public class DSETransformationRule<Match extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.IPatternMatch,Matcher extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.ViatraQueryMatcher<Match>>
extends org.eclipse.viatra.transformation.runtime.emf.rules.batch.BatchTransformationRule<Match,Matcher>
    An instance of this class is a specification of a graph transformation rule on a given metamodel. Such a rule consists of a left hand side (LHS), which is specified by an IQuerySpecification and a right hand side (RHS), which is specified by an IMatchProcessor.
